{"tid":985980,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［機已爆］Ace combat 7 點評， 無劇透","createTime":"2019-01-18T05:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T11:11:45.000Z","uid":33799,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"3b06a40b4bdac0ee13eacbf8af8a326c3ae75d81","tid":985980,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:57:59.000Z","msg":"畫面：第一個感覺係畫面質素係好靚好靚，地面建築同車都細緻好多，作為一個ace combat fan 好滿足<br />\n<br />\n操控性： 操控上我淨係用expert rolling, 咁就同前作無太大分別，好易上手。建議新手可以直接用expert, standard 反而限制左迴避動作，打後期你會好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n遊戲性：關卡總共20關（我無咩點卡關兩日搞掂），AI真係叻左好多，同埋做到無人機同有人機個分別。任務系統就無咩新意，但係感覺上有唔少係逼你用岩特殊武器或者機種先可以S到。不過機隻數量比較少，我諗有心刷可以一星期開哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯一問題係無online coop, 其實我對death match或者battle royale無咩興趣<br />\n<br />\n劇情：延續番以前故仔，個人覺得都帶到啲message出黎，會諗起以前個幾集啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋啲女好撚正<br />\n<br />\n結論： 舊作fans必買，新手唔急可以等有折先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4f4033774c181660d0983b5873d7cd7382fff1","tid":985980,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無人理"},{"pid":"274df9fc70a76f57ea01d810502a68b2d0c112cf","tid":985980,"uid":11703,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:26:26.000Z","msg":"等緊stream"},{"pid":"633f36da60e25e6ef9c81007dbcc4d5f356f3c1f","tid":985980,"uid":3656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:31:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">不過機隻數量比較少，我諗有心刷可以一星期開哂</span><br />\n<br />\n分明係想用DLC出新機體呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7d351bf692d27e391858952d78239bbf946207","tid":985980,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"633f36da60e25e6ef9c81007dbcc4d5f356f3c1f","tid":985980,"uid":365