PC ver"},{"pid":"786296369dd41649d3fb6629e89bfcaae9af5e4c","tid":985980,"uid":33799,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c4b1e882f706a5b24024c2463311a42eb45979d8","tid":985980,"uid":3591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:02:33.000Z","msg":"尋晚打第八關打到燥，係咁crash"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:00:04.000Z","msg":"我個陣用緊F/A, 我諗你係講緊有沙塵暴之後？ 如果打ground target有兩種方法：<br />\n<br />\n第一係keep 住低飛，你架機同個人夠定就無問題，唔好飛太快，但係容易俾UAV打。<br />\n<br />\n第二係飛高，高速飛到去指定區域，locate jor，垂直減速穿落去target，一射完即刻抽頭，避到UAV<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fe74cf9d373036ba42c83639e49279840e1be9","tid":985980,"uid":32168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T02:51:13.000Z","msg":"Mission 12巨石陣點過？"},{"pid":"38807489183cc8140e504b51d742694309421232","tid":985980,"uid":33799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"42fe74cf9d373036ba42c83639e49279840e1be9","tid":985980,"uid":32168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T02:51:13.000Z","msg":"Mission 12巨石陣點過？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T03:09:53.000Z","msg":"我打呢關個陣用F22, 有對地炸彈用，用黎慳正常彈。最緊要快，ground target 優先打AD tank, air target打bomber/ attack craft 。我每邊一清淨一兩架就即刻去第二度幫拖。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後打無人機就要小心，一發一發咁射會好啲，打無人機最忌係打死一架，第一發唔中見佢向左右避緊，就可以即刻轉lock打前面既，通常前面個架無俾你lock住唔會有迴避動作，一射完即刻抽頭搵第二架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eabce8880d384684b6d40a142912909160db61b","tid":985980,"uid":61325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T03:47:30.000Z","msg":"自從玩左gtav d 空戰之後<br />\n一直都想玩空戰game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻洗唔洗話買飛機手制玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d